000Z","msg":"個個都一路係度呃自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T02:45:25.000Z","msg":"夜行人吹哨子, 寫篇文為自己壯膽<br />\n佢覺得年審視獨立稅地位係虛招<br />\n因為實招係2020要普選立法會/行政長官, 呢個係一個威脅<br />\n就係要中共退場"},{"pid":"cea9ca60557eed84ef20e3c81f39c929693ca5a6","tid":1761391,"uid":104106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T02:51:37.000Z","msg":"因為份法案唔係淨為制裁,<br />\n1.定期檢討香港關係法, 包括法治完整,警暴, 人權同有冇利用自己特殊地位搵美國佬笨,轉運北韓,伊朗. 竊取知識產權<br />\n由國務卿話事-今期係Mike Pompeo 請自求多福<br />\n2.因參與由2014示威至今而定罪嘅人, 攞VISA 係不受影響.<br />\n即係話你法庭廢啊, 有班紅底法官揸旗啊. 有班綠曱甴為非作歹<br />\n遲D連其他國家都立自己版本嘅&lt;HKHRDA&gt;都唔會因案底而冇得走"},{"pid":"ac3d979d1c493989d8ce2723ad4362ff9129e430","tid":1761391,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T03:03:33.000Z","msg":"Merry Christmas <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf6ce089748596c562757b54c173be50282ccb92","tid":1761391,"uid":11148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T03:13:09.000Z","msg":"特朗普日前就表示，可能會以總統的權力，否決《香港人權與民主法案》，<span style=\"color: red;\">原因是習近平是他的「好朋友」。不知香港的反對派聽了這樣的話有何感想</span><br />\n<br />\n屍廢青應該真心蠢撚黎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nbtw法國屍廢青燈力直逼燒山,佢話唔會發生就一定會發生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73c7a9d3be91785eeccbed45520bb247a0a30cf3","tid":1761391,"uid":324602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T03:16:58.000Z","msg":"xi is my best friend<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b2e935e7b54a28bc60286eca9ab28fd653a1edf","tid":1761391,"uid":238415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T03:25:59.000Z","msg":"去試下咪知虛實lo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}